#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag5.7:4.1"
msgid "5.7. Gayākassapattheragāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc345"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts345"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.7:5.1"
msgid "“Pāto <span class=\"var\" title=\"majjhantikaṃ (bj, s2, s3, pts1) | majjhaṇhikaṃ (pts2)\" id=\"note193\">majjhanhikaṃ</span> sāyaṃ,"
msgstr "Three times a day—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:5.2"
msgid "tikkhattuṃ divasassahaṃ;"
msgstr "Morning, midday, and evening—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:5.3"
msgid "Otariṃ udakaṃ sohaṃ,"
msgstr "I went down into the water at Gayā,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:5.4"
msgid "gayāya gayaphagguyā."
msgstr "For the Gayā spring festival."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc346"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts346"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.7:6.1"
msgid "‘Yaṃ mayā pakataṃ pāpaṃ,"
msgstr "“Whatever bad things I’ve done"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:6.2"
msgid "pubbe aññāsu jātisu;"
msgstr "In previous births,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:6.3"
msgid "Taṃ dānīdha pavāhemi’,"
msgstr "I’ll now wash away right here”—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:6.4"
msgid "evaṃdiṭṭhi pure ahuṃ."
msgstr "This is the view I previously held."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc347"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts347"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.7:7.1"
msgid "Sutvā subhāsitaṃ vācaṃ,"
msgstr "Having heard the well-spoken words"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:7.2"
msgid "dhammatthasahitaṃ padaṃ;"
msgstr "Regarding the Dhamma and the goal,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:7.3"
msgid "Tathaṃ yāthāvakaṃ atthaṃ,"
msgstr "I wisely reflected"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:7.4"
msgid "yoniso paccavekkhisaṃ."
msgstr "On the true, essential goal."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc348"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts348"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.7:8.1"
msgid "Ninhātasabbapāpomhi,"
msgstr "I’ve washed away all bad things"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:8.2"
msgid "nimmalo payato suci;"
msgstr "I’m stainless, clean, pristine;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:8.3"
msgid "Suddho suddhassa dāyādo,"
msgstr "The pure heir of the pure one,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:8.4"
msgid "putto buddhassa oraso."
msgstr "A rightful son of the Buddha."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc349"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts349"></a>
msgctxt "thag5.7:9.1"
msgid "Ogayhaṭṭhaṅgikaṃ sotaṃ,"
msgstr "When I plunged into the eight-fold stream,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:9.2"
msgid "sabbapāpaṃ pavāhayiṃ;"
msgstr "All bad things were washed away."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:9.3"
msgid "Tisso vijjā ajjhagamiṃ,"
msgstr "I’ve attained the three knowledges,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag5.7:9.4"
msgid "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan”ti."
msgstr "And fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag5.7:10.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

